  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Get ready to go for the gold! It's time to hit the arena for the LITTLEST PET SHOP Biggest Stars competition--and this time your pets are in the spotlight! Ten fun and challenging mini-games are your pets' tickets to the big time. Practice makes perfect as you help your pets become the best gymnasts, models, ice skaters, dancers, flyers, fashion designers, and more. Then pack up their cute team uniforms and the dozens of super-fun accessories you've customized because it's time to hit the road! The Biggest Stars competition is the event of the year, when the pet-triplet judges look for teams that are a triple threat; cute, peppy and totally talented! Good thing that with your help, all your LITTLEST PET SHOP pet's Biggest Stars dreams really can come true!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ]
